":1813,"type":1117,"uid":1800,"updated_at":1836},73235,[1785],{"id":1786,"name":78,"url":1787,"thumbnail":78,"created_at":1788,"tags":78,"author":1789,"type":1072,"filename":1790,"description":1791,"750x750px":1792,"160x90px":1793,"365x225px":1794,"100x100px":1795,"760xautopx":1796,"1200x675px":1797,"article_id":1783},202382,"https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/gostynska/articles/image/4346f73a-3e23-4483-9058-2be81f1dfb99","2026-03-10 16:28:59","Urząd Miejski w Pogorzeli","4346f73a-3e23-4483-9058-2be81f1dfb99","Organizacje i kluby sportowe  podpisały umowę z burmistrz D. Wyzuj na przyznane dotacje","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/gostynska/articles/image/04fc6e7e-e209-4b55-b23d-0a3eca7059e3","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/gostynska/articles/image/d0d6f36e-193d-4b60-a44e-4a6be358606a","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/gostynska/articles/image/3395ac16-52f0-4ad1-8bdd-e463728a2580","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/gostynska/articles/image/6dc171a6-1142-4f17-aed3-81f408aa4ef2","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/gostynska/articles/image/40b8c115-36ca-487d-aa6b-cd8d918361d9","https://storage.googleapis.com/poludniowaoficyna-pbem/gostynska/articles/image/d526c015-21e9-4681-a34f-b864ca6085f7",[111],{"id":75,"frequency":75},"pYsG0LYLj400LAXFdnHn",[1802,1803,1804,1805,1089,1806,1807,1808,1809,1628,1810],"rozdano","kilkadziesiat","tysiecy","zlotych","co","beda","przeznaczone","pieniadze","budzetu","Treningi piłkarskie i udział w rozgrywkach, szkolenia sportowe, zakup sprzętu sportowego oraz nagród – to tylko niektóre zadania w zakresie rozwoju aktywności fizycznej, jakie planują wprowadzić w życie sportowe organizacje z gminy Pogorzela. Mogą wykorzystać na to dotacje przyznane z budżetu gminy.",{"title":1813,"description":1814,"keywords":1815,"fb_cover":1816,"fb_title":75,"fb_description":75},"Rozdano kilkadziesiąt tysięcy złotych. Na co będą przeznaczone pieniądze z budżetu?","Treningi piłkarskie i udział w rozgrywkach, szkolenia sportowe, zakup sprzętu sportowego i nagród na imprezy – to tylko niektóre zadania w zakresie rozwoju aktywności fizycznej, jakie planują zorganizować sportowe organizacje z gminy Pogorzela. Mogą wykorzystać na to dotacje przyznane z budżetu gminy.","dotacja, gmina Pogorzela, budżet, sport , szkolenie",{"value":1817},{"filename":75,"name":75,"tags":75,"thumbnail":75,"type":75,"url":75},"2026-03-10 16:29:49","https://gostynska.pl/wiadomosci/rozdano-kilkadziesiat-tysiecy-zlotych-na-co-beda-przeznaczone-pieniadze-z-budzetu/pYsG0LYLj400LAXFdnHn","rozdano-kilkadziesiat-tysiecy-zlotych-na-co-beda-przeznaczone-pieniadze-z-budzetu","Rozdano im kilkadziesiąt tysięcy",[1823,1824,1825,1826,1827],"sport ","dotacja","gmina Pogorzela","szkolenie","budżet",[1829,1830,1831,1833,1834],{"tag":1823,"slug":156},{"tag":1824,"slug":1824},{"tag":1825,"slug":1832},"gmina-pogorzela",{"tag":1826,"slug":1826},{"tag":1827,"slug":1835},"budzet","2026-03-11 13:53:16",["Reactive",1838],{"ads":9,"aid":1839,"alternative_gallery_style":9,"attachments":1840,"author":1428,"author_info":20,"category":1853,"comments":9,"comments_auth":9,"content":78,"created_by":1430,"created_by_name":78,"custom_html":75,"featured":33,"gallery_ads":1854,"gallery_picked":14,"id":1855,"is_advertisement":33,"is_photostory":33,"is_pool":33,"multiportal":75,"view_type":75,"is_redirect":33,"keywords":1856,"lead":1866,"locked":33,"meta":1867,"parent_domain":75,"parent_id":75,"photostory_added":14,"pool_picked":75,"pool_under_photostory":14,"premium":33,"published":20,"published_at":1877,"quiz_picked":75,"recommended":33,"redirect_url":75,"self_url":1878,"show_quiz_cover":14,"slug":1879,"sponsored":14,"short_title":1880,"tags":1881,"tagsRaw":1886,"title":1868,"type":1117,"uid":1855,"updated_at":1895},73229,[1841],{"id":1842,"name":78,"url":1843,"thumbnail":78,"created_at":1844,"tags":78,"author":1845,"type":1072,"filename":1846,"description":78,"7